I remember @_leesha_ and I thought we would simply love, travel the world and build an empire together. We never imagined having a little one that would steal our hearts. Unconditional Love… We never saw you coming @baby_cru_ , but boy are we happy that you showed up in our lives. 

Your mommy and I are so happy to have you and can’t believe you are here to wake us up in the mornings! Who needs an alarm clock?! Lol

We love you so much Bubs! Can’t believe we have a 1 Year Old! Love you @baby_cru_  #happybirthday
